SUMMARY:MELT ICE WITH LOVE! Meditation Retreat @ The Melon Ball
DESCRIPTION:Join Us for MELT ICE WITH LOVE! \nExperience the power of the MELT (myofascial energetic length technique) Method combined with an energizing and empowering Heart-Coherence Meditation at this in-person event. It’s all about easing tension\, boosting your energy\, and connecting with your heart’s rhythm. Let’s generate lots of love and send it to our friends in Minnesota! Whether you’re new or experienced\, come ready to relax\, rejuvenate\, and melt away stress with love and positive intentions. Don’t miss out on this unique journey. If you are a seasoned practitioner of the MELT Method\, please bring your own MELT Method soft roller. Everyone else: please wear comfortable clothes and bring a yoga mat\, sheepskin or sleeping pad\, blanket\, pillow\, and water. DONATION BASED. All proceeds benefit the Minnesota Interfaith Coalition on Immigration (http://www.mnicom.org). \nAs Wayne Dyer\, the Heart Math Institute\, and so many other visionary individuals and institutions have reminded us\, “One individual who lives and vibrates to the energy of pure love and reverence for all of life will counterbalance the negativity of 750\,000 individuals who calibrate at the lower\, weakening levels.” Let’s see what we can do when we come together with a strong intention to make a positive impact on our world!
URL:https://thedirt.online/event/melt-ice-with-love-meditation-retreat-the-melon-ball/
LOCATION:Melon Ball – Watermelon Music\, 1970 Lake Blvd\, Suite #1\, Davis\, California\, 95616\, United States
CATEGORIES:Community,Fitness
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://thedirt.online/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/MeltIce-scaled.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Watermelon Music":MAILTO:watermelonmusicdavis@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
