SUMMARY:General Meeting with Guest Speaker: karen Bolaños
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260310T020000Z
DTEND;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260310T030000Z
UID:af124c5231b6bbf144205e8c0755955512172025_7:07:20_PM@campusgroups.com
DESCRIPTION:We are excited to welcome Karen Bolaños\, Career Development 
 Operations Manager at the UC Davis Graduate School of Management\, as our 
 guest speaker. Karen is a proud Aggie alum who supports the GSM career cen
 ter by managing strategic career development operations\, data systems\, a
 nd research that help students succeed. Prior to her current role\, she sp
 ent seven years in the tech industry working in operations and education. 
 Join us to hear about Karen’s career path\, insights into career develop
 ment and organizational strategy\, and get the chance to ask questions abo
 ut navigating professional opportunities both during and after college. --
 - Event Details: https://aggielife.ucdavis.edu/rsvp?id=907634
URL:https://aggielife.ucdavis.edu/rsvp?id=907634
X-SOURCE:UC Davis CampusGroups
END:VEVENT
