DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260313T114500
SUMMARY:Healing Arts 6-Session Workshop
DESCRIPTION:Pence Adult Art Programs\nThe Pence’s 6-session Healing Arts workshop uses art as a healing language for those experiencing grief from the loss of a loved one. Through the process of art making\, participants will have opportunities for discussion\, education\, and connecting with peers in a safe and supportive space in the Pence Learning Center under the guidance of facilitators Amy Vidra and Lyndsey Rocca.\n\nREGISTRATION ONLINE IS REQUIRED IN ADVANCE through the Pence Gallery's website\, and space is limited to the first 8 participants who register. Participants must be 18 or older\, and no art experience is necessary. This program is generously sponsored by Bob & Joanne Andresen.\n\nHealing Arts 6-Session Workshop\nFridays\\\, 10\\-11:45 AM \\| Mar\\. 13\\\, 20\\\, 27 & Apr\\. 3\\\, 10\\\, 17\n$25 Members\, $35 Non-Members (all materials included)\n\n**Reminder - an RSVP on Meetup does NOT count as registration. Registration is required in advance through the [Pence’s website](https://pencegallery.org/education/programs/workshops-and-classes/).**\n\nPlease note that when registering for this program\, you are signing up for all 6 sessions. If you are unable to attend one or more of the sessions\, please let us know in advance.\n\nAny questions? Email pencegallery@gmail.com
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/pence-adult-art-programs/events/313069204/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260126T200432Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260126T200432Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/3/1/8/0/600_532452672.jpeg
END:VEVENT
