SUMMARY:Free Yoga Practice
DESCRIPTION:Iama Embodied Community\n🌀 **Move with intention. Connect with your body. Celebrate community.**\n\nJoin us every **Thursday at 6 PM** for an embodied yoga practice designed to help you release tension\, ground yourself\, and cultivate presence. This is a trauma-informed\, all-levels class\, no prior yoga experience needed. Expect a Hatha-Vinyasa flow\, breathwork\, and a space to listen to your body’s wisdom.\n\n🌿 **Every last Thursday of the month\, stay after class for a community potluck dinner!**\n\n📍 **Location**: 727 T St. Sacramento CA 95811\n✨ **All our events are free. Donations are welcome.**\n📩 **Questions? Reach out at** embody.iama@gmail.com\n🔗 **Follow us on Instagram:** [@embody.iama](https://www.instagram.com/embody.iama)
