DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260321T160000
SUMMARY:Gel Printing Workshop with Sara Post
DESCRIPTION:Pence Adult Art Programs\nUnder the guidance of artist Sara Post\, students will explore the ins and out of gel printing. Participants will experiment with layering\, masks\, stencils\, and other gel printing techniques\, as well as work with a variety of papers. Gel prints\, beautiful in themselves\, are also a wonderful way to make handmade papers for collage or under layers for painting. Students will leave this class with a portfolio of prints to display on their own or to use in making other artworks.\n\nGel Printing Workshop with Sara Post\nSaturday\, March 21\, 9:30 AM - 4 PM\n$170 Members\, $190 Non-Members (Materials not included)\n\n**Registration is required in advance through the Pence's website ([CLICK HERE](https://pencegallery.org/education/programs/workshops-and-classes/)).**\n\nAny questions? Email pencegallery@gmail.com.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/pence-adult-art-programs/events/313287945/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260210T003150Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260210T003150Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/c/8/7/d/600_532671325.jpeg
END:VEVENT
