BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Davis Chamber": "https://web.davischamber.com/events/The%20Pence%20Joins%20Yolo%20Fest%20This%20Spring%20-5700/details"}
X-SOURCE-ID:davis_chamber
SUMMARY:The Pence Joins Yolo Fest This Spring!
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260327T113000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260329T170000
UID:8e1c0419becf460c9aee796d2b0d3eb4@davischamber.com
DESCRIPTION:Community Event\n\nThe Pence Joins Yolo Fest This Spring!\n\nT
 he Pence Gallery\, a unique nonprofit art gallery highlighting local & reg
 ional artists\, is participating in the county-wide Yolo Fest this spring.
  From March 27-29\, 2026\, Yolo Fest celebrates the region’s agriculture
 \, music\, arts\, culture\, farm-to-table food\, craft beverages\, recreat
 ion\, and local hospitality. \n\nThe Pence Gallery in Davis will be open 
 with three spectacular art exhibits from 11:30 AM - 5 PM\, and admission i
 s free to view these displays by these visual artists:\n\nManuel Fernando 
 Rios: When They Reminisce Over You\n\nFebruary 7 - March 29\n\nIn his exhi
 bit\, Rios shares his interest in themes that explore his Chicano heritage
 \, as well as his family’s history and experiences. Blurring the line be
 tween naturalism and abstraction\, the artist embraces the use of complex 
 design patterns\, photography\, and text to make a powerful statement. \n
 \nAssorted Flavors: Pence Member Exhibit\n\nMarch 13 - April 16\n\nView 40
  works of art created by Pence Members in this widely ranging annual displ
 ay of paintings\, photographs\, textiles\, and more. \n\nBarbara Prodaniu
 k: Myths in Mud\n\nMarch 13 - April 26\n\nProdaniuk is a ceramic artist wh
 ose work is inspired by the forest\, meadows\, and waterways of the Trucke
 e area. She explores stories carried by the animals and artifacts found in
  these environments. \n\nSpecial Weekend Activities\n\nSelf-guided Scaven
 ger Hunt:\n\nMarch 28-29\, 11:30 AM - 4:30 PM\n\nFree to participate!\n\nJ
 oin us for a fun\, art-themed scavenger hunt at the gallery by exploring t
 he Pence’s exhibits. Complete all of the clues for the chance to be ente
 red in a raffle to win a $25 gift certificate to the Pence gift store! A r
 affle winner will be selected and contacted at 4:30 PM on both Saturday an
 d Sunday.\n\nPrintmaking for All Ages\n\nSunday\, March 29\, 1-3 PM\n\n$5 
 Members | $10 Non-Members (per person\, all materials included)\n\nIn this
  workshop\, printmaking is made easy! Learn how to create bold and colorfu
 l block prints using a Styrofoam plate\, printmaking ink\, and a few simpl
 e tricks and techniques. This is a drop-in program for all ages\, and no s
 ign-ups are required in advance. Children ages 5 and up may participate if
  they are accompanied by an adult.
LOCATION:212 D Street\, Davis\, CA 95616
URL:https://web.davischamber.com/events/The%20Pence%20Joins%20Yolo%20Fest%
 20This%20Spring%20-5700/details
X-SOURCE:Davis Chamber of Commerce
END:VEVENT
