SUMMARY:Conscious Conversations & Embodied Listening  
DESCRIPTION:Iama Embodied Community\nThis is a spiritual community that honors the body’s wisdom and lived experience. Whether you’re healing from religious trauma\, deconstructing beliefs\, exploring spirituality\, or just want to be with other conscious persons\, this space is for you.\n\nExpect conscious conversations\, meditation\, breathwork\, sound healing\, and other somatic practices to help reconnect with ourselves and each other.\n\nwe share a potluck dinner every last Monday of the month.\n\n📅 **Date & Time**: Mondays 6-8 PM\n📍 **Location**: 727 T St. Sacramento\, Ca\, 95811\n💜 **All our events are free\, donations supported.**\n✨ **No prior experience or spiritual beliefs necessary.**\n📩 **RSVP/ Questions? Reach out at** embody.iama@gmail.com\n🔗 **Follow us on Instagram:** [@embody.iama](https://www.instagram.com/embody.iama)\n\nPS: we meet in the social hall of Parkview Presbyterian Church. Please find us through the back entrance\, the brown gate on Solons alley. You may park in the back\, move the orange post to park and please return it when you leave.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/mindful-embodied-spirituality/events/313060116/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260126T055156Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260126T055156Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/e/4/3/9/600_531418425.jpeg
END:VEVENT
