BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Davis Downtown": "https://davisdowntown.com/event/davis-farmers-market-year-round-fresh-local-in-central-park-50th-anniversary-year/2026-04-01/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:davis_downtown
SUMMARY:Davis Farmers Market – Year-Round Fresh & Local in Central Park 
 (50th Anniversary Year!)
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260401T150000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260401T180000
UID:10000237-1775055600-1775066400@davisdowntown.com
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate 50 years of community and bounty at the Davis Farmer
 s Market in 2026! This iconic\, award-winning market is the heartbeat of D
 avis – bringing together local farmers\, artisans\, bakers\, food vendor
 s\, and makers every week. Wednesdays: 3:00 PM – 6:00 PM (September–Ma
 rch)\; 4:00 PM – 8:00 PM Picnic in the Park with live music (April–Aug
 ust) Shop the freshest seasonal produce\, farm-fresh eggs/meats/cheese\, a
 rtisan crafts\, hot prepared foods\, coffee\, baked goods\, and more! All 
 grown or made right here in our region. Enjoy live music (especially durin
 g summer Picnic in the Park Wednesdays)\, family activities\, SNAP matchin
 g programs\, and the lively downtown energy that makes it a favorite gathe
 ring spot for residents\, UC Davis students\, families\, and visitors. Fre
 e entry – bring your bags and support local agriculture\, sustainability
 \, and small businesses! Rain or shine\, it’s always a great day out. Sp
 ecial 2026 highlights: 50th anniversary celebrations throughout the year. 
 Don’t miss the big community event on August 1!
LOCATION:Central Park\, 301 C St.\, Davis\, CA\, 95616\, United States
URL:https://davisdowntown.com/event/davis-farmers-market-year-round-fresh-
 local-in-central-park-50th-anniversary-year/2026-04-01/
X-SOURCE:Davis Downtown
END:VEVENT
