DESCRIPTION:Join us on the second Thursday of each month for our Governing
  Board of Directors meeting. The meeting is open to all interested. Stay u
 p-to-date on business and initiatives related to downtown Davis\, and the 
 opportunity to provide public comment will be available. Meetings are curr
 ently held virtually on the Zoom platform from 9:00am to 10:00am. If you a
 re interested in attending\, please contact us at info@davisdowntown.com t
 o request a Zoom meeting invitation. To view\, download and/or print Board
  of Directors meeting agendas or minutes\, click on the following link: ht
 tps://davisdowntown.com/agendas-meeting-information. Meeting locations and
  times are subject to change.
