SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260309T000533Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260409T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260409T114500
SUMMARY:Healing Arts One-Time Workshop
DESCRIPTION:Pence Adult Art Programs\nPart of the Pence's Healing Arts Program and run by facilitator Amy Vidra\, this one-time workshop focuses more broadly on themes related to depression\, anxiety\, or major life changes. Through the process of art making\, participants will have opportunities for discussion\, education\, and connecting with peers in a safe and supportive space.\n\nREGISTRATION ONLINE IS REQUIRED IN ADVANCE through the Pence Gallery's website\, and space is limited to the first 8 participants who register. Participants must be 18 or older\, and no art experience is necessary. This program is generously sponsored by Bob & Joanne Andresen.\n\nHealing Arts One-Time Workshop\nThursday\, April 9\, 10-11:45 AM\n$5 Members\, $10 Non-Members (all materials included)\n\n**Reminder - an RSVP on Meetup does NOT count as registration. Registration is required in advance through the [Pence’s website (CLICK HERE)](https://pencegallery.org/education/programs/workshops-and-classes/).**\n\n\\*If you register for this session and are unable to attend\, please let us know in advance.\n\nAny questions? Email pencegallery@gmail.com.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/pence-adult-art-programs/events/313610437/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260302T233409Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260302T233409Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/a/9/8/9/600_532483401.jpeg
END:VEVENT
