X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Meetup: Yolo Board Game Gathering": "https://www.meetup.com/yolo-county-board-game-gathering/events/kwnqstyjcgbtb/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:meetup_board_games
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Yolo Board Game Gathering
UID:event_kwnqstyjcgbtb@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260309T000533Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260415T170000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260415T210000
SUMMARY:Weekly Game Night at Blue Note
DESCRIPTION:Yolo County Board Game Gathering\nUpdate 8/14/25:\n**We're still active**\, but we primarily use Discord to chat and plan events. (See group description for invite link.)\n\nWe still meet every Wednesday for board games at Blue Note Brewing Company. We'll have a handful of tables reserved near the back\; just look for the pile of board games.\n\nPeople usually start arriving around 5pm\, and games start whenever people are ready. Blue Note closes at 9pm\, and although we have a 5-10 minute grace period there\, you should be in the process of final scoring by 9\, or else pack it up and play again another day.\n\nGame night is open to all ages! Blue Note is a brewery\, not a bar\, so there's no restriction against minors. In addition to their crafted-in-house beer selection\, water and sodas are available.\n\nYou're not required to buy anything in order to join us\, but we do encourage you to support local businesses. Blue Note's chef team makes a mean pizza\, and there are other nearby downtown restaurants and businesses.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/yolo-county-board-game-gathering/events/kwnqstyjcgbtb/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20250814T213413Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20250814T213413Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/a/b/2/a/600_496663818.jpeg
END:VEVENT
