SUMMARY:Blood on the Clocktower at Blue Note
DESCRIPTION:Yolo County Board Game Gathering\nThe first Wednesday of every month\, we play _Blood on the Clocktower_\, a social deduction game in the vein of Werewolf/Mafia/The Resistance\, with a few twists!\n\nWe'll have a circle of chairs reserved inside Blue Note\, near the back\, with a Yolo County Board Game Gathering sign on the table. Just say hello\, and we'll show you some games\, pull some players together\, and get to having fun!\n\nWe also usually have a few tables of players playing other board games\, if social deduction isn't your bag!\n\nGet a feel for Blood on the Clocktower here: https://youtu.be/4sfa8_kNxsQ
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/yolo-county-board-game-gathering/events/mxnqstyjchbjb/
